OL,3,CCivil process 'not working' for
OL,4,Cvictims of Glenanne gang
OL,6,FA solicitor representing families
OL,7,Fmurdered by the loyalist Glenanne gang
OL,8,Fsays the civil process isn't working.
OL,10,FGavin Booth was speaking as relatives
OL,11,Fof those murdered by the gang were
OL,12,Fback in court.
OL,14,FFor many it is a protracted legal
OL,15,Fbattle over killings by a loyalist
OL,16,Fparamilitary group with alleged links
OL,17,Fto members of the security forces
OL,18,Fduring the 1970s.
