OL,4,Cvictims of Glenanne gang
OL,6,FMore than a dozen civil cases are now
OL,7,Fbeing heard by one judge, but today
OL,8,Ffamilies said the system isn't working.
OL,10,F"The judge is frustrated at having to
OL,11,Flist these cases and constantly try to
OL,12,Fget them dealt with, but unfortunately
OL,13,Fwe're not at a stage where these can
OL,14,Fbe dealt with as quickly as they can,"
OL,15,FGavin Booth said.
OL,17,F"We think something needs to be done
OL,18,Fto change this.
