OL,4,Cvictims of Glenanne gang
OL,6,FMeanwhile the PSNI Chief Constable
OL,7,Fsaid police are "failing" victims in
OL,8,Fdealing with the legacy of Northern
OL,9,FIreland's troubled past because of a
OL,10,Flack of funding and an agreed approach.
OL,12,FJon Boutcher said some #160 million
OL,13,Fhas been spent on legacy over the last
OL,14,Ften years.
OL,16,FThis includes investigating legacy
OL,17,Foffences, staff to provide
OL,18,Fdocumentation for legal cases, and
OL,19,Fdealing with civil claims.
