OL,6,FHe also said the annual cost of
OL,7,Fdealing with legacy is equivalent to
OL,8,F400 police officers, at a time when
OL,9,Fthe PSNI is severely under-staffed.
OL,11,FMr Boutcher recently halted
OL,12,Fresearchers working on any cases apart
OL,13,Ffrom preparation for the next stage of
OL,14,Fthe Omagh Bombing Inquiry, which will
OL,15,Fstart in June.
OL,17,FHe said his staff are meeting legal
OL,18,Frepresentatives for victims over the
OL,19,Fdelays and legal processes.
