OL,6,FAddressing the Northern Ireland
OL,7,FPolicing Board, Mr Boutcher also
OL,8,Fdescribed reputational damage being
OL,9,Fcaused to the PSNI over legacy, saying
OL,10,Fit is feeding off the "outdated and
OL,11,Fdangerous narrative" of those behind
OL,12,Fanti-police posters.
OL,14,F"The legacy of our past continues to
OL,15,Fplay a significant part in providing a
OL,16,Fbarrier to trust and confidence in
OL,17,Fpolicing in Northern Ireland. Other
OL,18,Fthan some marginal funding for
OL,19,Finquests, the PSNI is not funded to
OL,20,Faddress legacy," he said.
