OL,6,F"We have insufficient resources in the
OL,7,Fdepartments that deal with legacy that
OL,8,Fresulted in us failing victims and
OL,9,Fcommunities.
OL,11,F"Those failures include slow and
OL,12,Fpartial information disclosure, the
OL,13,Finappropriate categorisation and
OL,14,Fmanagement of sensitive information,
OL,15,Fand criminal investigations either not
OL,16,Fbeing completed or undertaken in a
OL,17,Ftimely fashion."
