OL,6,FMr Boutcher said he is not criticising
OL,7,Fofficers and staff who deal with
OL,8,Flegacy, and they have done an
OL,9,F"incredible job with the resources
OL,10,Fthat they have".
OL,12,F"They continue to do their very best,
OL,13,Fbut they've been let down by the
OL,14,Fabsence of a plan and the lack of
OL,15,Fresourcing and funds to properly
OL,16,Faddress legacy litigation, inquests
OL,17,Fand criminal investigations," he said.
