OL,6,FOutlining the cost of legacy, Mr
OL,7,FBoutcher said in total the PSNI have
OL,8,Fincurred costs of #160 million on
OL,9,Flegacy matters in the last 10 years,
OL,10,Fand there could potentially be further
OL,11,Fcases going on for decades.
OL,13,F"Annually, the cost of legacy equates
OL,14,Fto approximately 400 police officers,"
OL,15,Fhe told the Policing Board.
OL,17,F"This is a shocking figure at a time
OL,18,Fwhen the service faces unprecedented
OL,19,Foperational pressure.
