OL,6,F"There are over 1,100 outstanding
OL,7,Fcivil actions against the PSNI. That's
OL,8,Fup from 150 in 2014, the figure is
OL,9,Flikely to continue rising.
OL,11,F"Looking ahead, we expect the cost of
OL,12,Four involvement in the Omagh Bombing
OL,13,FInquiry to be between #12 million and
OL,14,F#15 million."
OL,16,FHe also said they expect that working
OL,17,Fwith the Independent Commission for
OL,18,FReconciliation and Information
OL,19,FRecovery (ICRIR) will cost #1.5
