OL,6,F"The PSNI is not funded for these
OL,7,Fissues," he said.
OL,9,F"It's time for an honest conversation
OL,10,Fabout the PSNI and how the PSNI and
OL,11,Flegacy is actually funded.
OL,13,F"We need a dedicated, properly
OL,14,Fresourced approach to legacy, which is
OL,15,Fdistinct from the day-to-day work of
OL,16,Fthe PSNI."
